{
  "texts": [
    "Online Preference Learning Data We follow prior work (Meng et al., 2024; Xu et al., 2024b) and consider using data from UltraFeedback (Cui et al., 2023) as prompts.",
    "We then sample multiple responses from π θ and use Pair-RM (Jiang et al., 2023b) as a judge to obtain preference pairs.",
    "This results in an online collected dataset of 60k in size.",
    "Unless otherwise indicated, all dataset subsets related to online learning are randomly sampled from this 60k dataset.",
    "Evaluation Benchmarks We assess our models using OpenLLM (Beeching et al., 2023) and Arena-Hard-Auto (Li et al., 2024)."
  ]
}